Package: liads
Title: LinkedIn Ad Library API Client
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Fabio", "Votta", , "fabio.votta@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3143-7315"))
Description: A comprehensive R client for the LinkedIn Ad Library API. Provides 
    functions for OAuth 2.0 authentication, querying ads by keyword/advertiser/country/date,
    automatic pagination, and robust data processing. Supports all official API 
    parameters and returns structured data frames with detailed ad information,
    targeting data, and impression statistics.
